## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="22c52-151"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>在必须 `Fill` 为两个或更多对象调用方法的应用程序中，这种实现非常有用 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22c52-151">This implementation of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> can be useful in an application that must call the `Fill` method for two or more <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> objects.</span></span>  
  
   
  
