 <span data-ttu-id="22c52-152">下面的示例创建 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 并设置其一些属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22c52-152">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
